channel.title: Couple things with a 562
channel.description:
Hey guys, i'm looking for a decently experienced 562 with a couple problems i can't seem to fix, i tried of course so i'm not being lazy, but it just wont work.
2 examples of problems i have is:
1. Dragon claws spec-hits normal, then after the last hit of a spec, it hits a 5th hit that hits like thousands.
2. Any Ice spell in ancients, as in barrage, blitz etc. Doesn't freeze the target, and theres no magicvsnpc.
Thanks if you can help, and if needed, you can have in game power, or a payment of some sort, thanks.
